lead_paragraph: Lexi Thompson shot an 8-under 64 Saturday in the third round of the LPGA Thailand to establish a four-stroke lead over Korean In Gee Chun at Siam Country Club.

headline.print_headline: Thompson Shoots 8-Under 64 to Lead LPGA Thailand
